OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fwarm sunshine this evening, then dry
OL,7,Fovernight. Low cloud and sea mist may
OL,8,Foccasionally affect western coasts,
OL,9,Fwith patchy fog forming in prone areas
OL,10,Finland. Staying mild in many coastal
OL,11,Fareas, but turning rather chilly in
OL,12,Frural spots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FAny fog quickly clearing, then
OL,15,Fsunny and very warm for most with
OL,16,Flight winds. Fresher on Irish Sea
OL,17,Fcoasts with a small chance of sea mist
OL,18,Fat times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
